			Fund Information
Fund Information for Financial Services ProvidersHere you will find valuable and useful information on our investment products. 
Details of tax treatment (PDF) (in German) of Credit Suisse funds with regard to
 EU retention.

The list of country permissions (PDF) shows the fund products, subfunds
and unit classes that are authorized for public sale in certain countries. 

The fund codes (PDF) section shows you all the codes of our investment products. 

Overview (PDF) of terms and conditions for Credits Suisse investment funds for partner banks. 

The list of annual financial statements, distributions and tax issues (PDF)
provides you with relevant information on our investment funds. 


